<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Zend_Session_SaveHandler_DbTable does not update properly on adapters with AUTO_QUOTE_IDENTIFIERS set to false. (This behavior was observed with an Oracle database.)</p>

<p>The root cause is that PRIMARY_TYPE_WHERECLAUSE quotes the identifier itself without regard to AUTO_QUOTE_IDENTIFIERS. The attached patch fixes this issue.</p>

    </div>
</div>

